{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-review-first-questions/glossary","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Potvrđujem da sam pročitao/la Rečnik.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"es-a1-review-first-questions","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ovaj glosariji je brzi referencijalni materijal za najvažnije reči i fraze iz sadržaja sa kojim ste radili u ovom modulu. Reči su organizovane po grupama i abecednom redosledu.</p>\n<h2>Pozdrav i identifikacija</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenas tardes</span> - Dobar dan</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Conocerte</span> - Susret sa tobom</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Encantada</span> / <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Encantado</span> - Drago mi je</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Hola</span> - Zdravo</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Igualmente</span> - Isto</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Me llaman</span> - Zovu me</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Mi nombre es</span> - Moje ime je</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Mucho gusto</span> - Drago mi je što sam te upoznao/upoznala</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h2>Pitanja</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿A qué te dedicas?</span> - Šta radiš?</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cómo te llamas?</span> - Kako se zoveš?</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cuántos años tienes?</span> - Koliko imaš godina?</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿De dónde eres?</span> - Odakle si?</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Y tú?</span> - A ti?</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Y vos?</span> - A ti? (Regionalna razlika)</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h2>Osobe i identifikacija</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Eres</span> - Ti si</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Soy</span> - Ja sam</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h2>Rad i umjetnost</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Analista</span> - Analitičar</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Datos</span> - Podaci</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Ingeniera</span> / <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Ingeniero</span> - Inženjer</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Junior</span> - Malo</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Recursos humanos</span> - Ljudski resursi</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Representante</span> - Predstavnik</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Software</span> - Programu</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h2>Mesto i priroda</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Colombia</span> - Kolumbija</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Colombiana</span> / <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Colombiano</span> - Mcolombia</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">De</span> - Kutoka</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">El Salvador</span> - El Salvador</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Guatemala</span> - Guatemala</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Guatemalteca</span> / <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Guatemalteco</span> - Guatemala</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Puerto Rico</span> - Puerto Rico</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Puertorriqueña</span> / <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Puertorriqueño</span> - Mpuerto Rico</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Salvadoreña</span> / <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Salvadoreño</span> - Msalvador</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h2>Broj</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta</span> - Trideset</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta y cinco</span> - Trideset pet</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta y seis</span> - Trideset šest</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintiuno</span> - Dvadeset i moje</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinticinco</span> - Dvadeset pet</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-review-first-questions/glossary"},"questions":[],"scene":null,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","tests":[],"title":"Rečnik","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-review-first-questions","dashedName":"glossary","certification":"a1-professional-spanish","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","chapter":"es-a1-chapter-greetings-and-introductions","module":"es-a1-module-first-questions","block":"es-a1-review-first-questions","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-quiz-first-questions/es-a1-quiz-first-questions","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-review-first-questions/grammar-highlights","id":"6910a2da60b9e944f13240a0","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":24,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-review-first-questions/glossary"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}